# Docker & Makefile

## Daily workflow

```bash
make dev          # Start full dev stack with hot reload
make dev-rebuild  # After package.json or Dockerfile changes
make dev-logs     # Follow app logs
make dev-shell    # Shell in app container (requires dev stack running)
make dev-migrate  # Run Drizzle migrations in container
```

## Host + DB only

```bash
make db-up        # PostgreSQL only
pnpm dev          # Nuxt on host
pnpm db:migrate   # Migrations on host
```

## Gotchas

- Dev image is **Debian-based** (not Alpine) — required for native modules
- Container startup runs `nuxt prepare` — do not remove
- After adding npm packages in Docker: `make dev-rebuild`
- Production binds `127.0.0.1:3000` for reverse proxy use

## Staging / production

```bash
make staging-migrate && make staging-up
make prod-migrate && make prod-up
```

See `Makefile` for full target list (`make help`).
